"2 pounds Yukon gold potatoes, peeled and cut into 1-inch pieces","7 teaspoons extra-virgin olive oil, divided","1/2 cup finely chopped shallots (about 3 small)","1 1/2 tablespoons sherry vinegar","2 teaspoons stone-ground mustard","1 teaspoon grated lemon rind","1 teaspoon fresh lemon juice","3/8 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","2 1/2 cups loosely packed arugula"